        <p>This is a somewhat responsive website for demo purposes only. This version has HTML and CSS spiced up with some PHP.
            The signup/login system was created based on a tutorial. It covers many different errors, for example empty inputs or wrong login information. 
            The database has AUTO_INCREMENT on the PRIMARY KEY usersId, so it automatically gives new accounts their own unique ID number.
